de_muanda 
by theDucer       
Version:02/18/05

Bomb/Defuse map in a dark and rainy church/castle setting

Terrorists:
Bomb either the mud hole (yeah it`s dangerous) in the castle
garden OR the grave of the holy bishop in the church.

Counter-Terrorists:
Prevent the Terrorists from fulfilling their mission

Additional information:
Once somebody steps into the mud hole or passes the room with
the fireplace, the GATE between the CT-Start and Bombside B
(mud hole) will be opened.

You can contact me via:			     Koenig12@gmx.de
